quran[23]{c,v,t}:
  12,7,"GomЙ—ii wonii e Yuusufa e musiЙ—Й“e makko Й“en, taskuyeeji wonannde lanndotooЙ“e Й“en"
  12,8,"tuma nde Й“e wi'unoo: \"Pellet ko Yuusufa e neene-gooto mun on Й“uraa yiЙ—eede ka ben-men dii enen, enen le ko en jamaa Й—uuЙ—uЙ“e. Pellet ben-men wonii e majjere Й“anngunde"
  12,9,"Waree Yuusufa maa feroЙ—on mo e leydi; yeeso ben mon ngon heeranoo on, wonton Й“aawo Й—um yimЙ“e moЖҙЖҙuЙ“e"
  12,10,"Gooto e maЙ“Й“e wi'i: \"Wata on waru Yuusufa, weddee mo ka niЙ“e woyndu yoga e seteeЙ“e hoccay mo, si on laatike gllooЙ“e"
  12,11,"ЖҒe wi'i: \"Ko an yo ben amen, ko heЙ“u-maa a hoolotaako men e fii Yuusufa? Menen le ko men laaЙ“amЙ“e mo reedu"
  12,12,"Accitidu-mo e amen o Гұaama, o fija. Menen ko men reenooЙ“e mo"
  12,13,"O maaki: \"Min no suninay lam nde yahdoton e makko; miЙ—o huli nde boyeeru ndu Гұaamata-mo ka welsindi-Й—on e makko"
  12,14,"ЖҒe wi'i: \"Pellet si saafaandu Гұaamii mo e hoore ko men jamaa Й—uuЙ—uЙ“e, haray ko men hayruЙ“e"
  12,15,"Nde Й“e yahdunoo e makko, Й“e fottani ukkugol mo ka niЙ“e woyndu, Men wahayini e makko: \"Ma a yeetitoyo Й“e Й—ee kuuЙ—e maЙ“Й“e hara Й“e so'aa anndude"
  12,16,ЖҒe arti ka ben maЙ“Й“e kiikiiЙ—e hiЙ“e woya
  12,17,"ЖҒe wi'i: \"Ko an yo baaben amen, menen men yehii meЙ—en adondira, men acci Yuusufa ka kaake amen saafaandu ndun Гұaami mo. A hoolotaako men non, hay si men wonii goonguЙ“e"
  12,18,"ЖҒe ardi e dolokke makko on hino moddi ЖҙiiЖҙam fenaande. O maaki: \"Si ko woni, wonkiiji mon Й—in cuЙ—inanii on fiyaaku. Ko muГұal moЖҙЖҙal [heddanii lam]! Ko Alla woni wallitorЙ—o e ko sifotoЙ—on kon"
  12,19,"SeteeЙ“e ari, Й“e nuli Жҙoogoowo maЙ“Й“e on, o jippini baagal makko ngal. O wi'i: \"Ee welВЁ-welo am! E hino paykum!\" ЖҒe suuЙ—iri mo keyee maЙ“Й“e. Alla non ko annduЙ—o ko Й“e gollata kon"
  12,20,"ЖҒe yeeyiri mo coggel famЙ—ungel: dirhamu-woy limotoo-koy. ЖҒe woni welsindiiЙ“e e fii makko"
  12,21,"SooduЙ—o mo on Misra wi'ani Й“eyngu makko: \"Teddin jipporde makko. Hino gasa ka o nafa en maa jogitoЙ—e mo Й“iЙ—Й—o\". Ko nii Men hoЙ—niri Yuusufa ka leydi fii yo Men anndin mo firo koyЙ—i. Alla ko fooluЙ—o e fiyaaku Makko on: kono ko Й“uri Й—uuЙ—ude e yimЙ“e Й“en anndaa"
  12,22,"Nde o yottinoo sagatalaaku makko, Men okki mo faamu e anndal. Ko wano nii Men yoЙ“irta moЖҙЖҙinooЙ“e Й“en"
  12,23,"On [debbo] mo on woni e suudu mun Й—aЙ“Й“iri mo hoore-makko. O soki baafe Й—en o wi'i: \"Mi heblanii-mo-ma!\" O maaki: \"Moolaare Alla! JeyЙ—o lam on moЖҙЖҙinii weerde am. Si ko woni, tooГұooЙ“e Й“en maletaake"
  12,24,"GomЙ—ii [debbo] on himmanii oon. Kanko kadi o himmanayno mo si wanaa o yi'ii hujja Joomi makko on. Ko nii [Men gerdiri] fii yo Men yiltu mo e bone e pankare. Pellet ko o jeyaaЙ—o e jeyaaЙ“e amen laЙ“Й“inaaЙ“e Й“en"
  12,25,"ЖҒe Й—iЙ—o kala Й“e adondiri ka baafal, o seekiri dolokke oya on Й“aawo. ЖҒe tawi moodi makko ka baafal. [debbo] on wi'i: \"Ko honЙ—um woni njoЙ“di on faalanaaЙ—o Й“eynguure maa nden bonki si wanaa yo soke [o leptiree] lepte muusuЙ—e"
  12,26,"[Yuusufu] maaki: \"Ko kanko Й—aЙ“Й“iri lam hoore-am\". TawanooЙ—o e yimЙ“e [debbo] on seeditii: \"Si tawii dolokke mum on ko yeeso seekiraa, haray ko [debbo] on goongi, kanko [gorko] on ko jeyaaЙ—o e fenuЙ“e Й“en"
  12,27,"Si tawii non dolokke makko on ka Й“aawo seekiraa, haray [debbo] on fenii, kanko [gorko] on ko o jeyaaЙ—o goonguЙ“e Й“en"
  12,28,"Nde [moodi makko] yi'unoo dolokke on ko Й“aawo seekori, o wi'i: \"ЖҠum ko jeyaaЙ—um e pewje mon! Pellet pewje mon Й—en ko haawniiЙ—e"
  12,29,"Yuusufa, Й—uurno gaayi e Й—um. An [debbo on], insinano junuubi(bakkaat) maa Й—in; tawde pellet a jeyaama e woopuЙ“e Й“en"